Author: tulipsandmothballs
Text: Thank you. I started seeing a therapist again but I haven’t felt like to happening. I’ll try and hang in there a little longer.

Author: lightsflicker
Text: When I started feeling like I don’t care if I live or die and I don’t care whether my eating disorder kills me, I reached out for help. It might take a long time, but if you do seek support now, you’ll begin to recover from the decades of self hatred. It sucks, I hope you feel better.
